snippet.title: BOWLOUT | Release Date - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Pin the date! BOWLOUT rolls onto Steam on January 7th, 2025.
▶ Steam page: [https://store.steampowered.com/app/2191160]
🗨 Twitter: [https://twitter.com/bowloutgame]

In BOWLOUT, you'll fight your way through a pin-infested bowling centre by throwing tons of bowling balls and crushing pins with powerful attacks.
Created and published by Sep Horsthuis and Quint Winter.

#gaming #pcgaming #indiegame #steam
